    # Z "It's too skimpy. People would pounce on you like hungry dogs."
    Z "Es demasiado escaso. La gente se abalanzaría sobre ti como perros hambrientos."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1017
translate spanish vfn_dress_one_c366a3e2:

    # Na "Even if I was walking hand in hand with my uncle...?"
    Na "¿Aunque caminara de la mano de mi tío...?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1018
translate spanish vfn_dress_one_9263adb3:

    # Na "People would admire him and his beautiful niece, don't you think?"
    Na "La gente le admiraría a él y a su preciosa sobrina, ¿no crees?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1021
translate spanish vfn_dress_one_ac4a03c8_2:

    # Na "Anyway, next one!"
    Na "En fin, ¡el siguiente!"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1025
translate spanish vfn_dress_one_97cae337:

    # Z "You are good looking and you clearly put effort in staying in shape."
    Z "Eres atractiva y está claro que te esfuerzas por mantenerte en forma."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1026
translate spanish vfn_dress_one_3f7784ce:

    # Z "There's no shame in being even more revealing."
    Z "No hay que avergonzarse de ser aún más atrevida."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1029
translate spanish vfn_dress_one_b244f31b:

    # Na "I see. But what if they took me for one of those public servants I've seen around...?"
    Na "Ya veo. Pero ¿y si me toman por una de esas empleadas públicas que he visto por ahí?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1032
translate spanish vfn_dress_one_ac4a03c8_3:

    # Na "Anyway, next one!"
    Na "En fin, ¡el siguiente!"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1038
translate spanish vfn80_27a0c3b2:

    # "She excitedly hurries over to her chest..."
    "Se apresura emocionada hacia su baúl..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1042
translate spanish vfn80_4e3f7f6e:

    # Na "Mom and Omar never seem to care about these things... if it was up to them, I'd walk around in a fully covering robe..."
    Na "Mamá y Omar nunca parecen preocuparse por estas cosas... si fuera por ellos, me pasearía con una bata que me cubriera por completo..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1043
translate spanish vfn80_0f192021:

