    "Echas un vistazo a su culo firme y melocotón..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1075
translate spanish vfn80_check_fd813a36:

    # Na "Almost done..."
    Na "Ya casi está..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1078
translate spanish vfn80_check_99412dda:

    # "Seeing her lithe, smooth legs in front of you, you're reminded of her mother, back when she was Nadia's age."
    "Al ver sus piernas ágiles y suaves delante de ti, te acuerdas de su madre, cuando tenía la edad de Nadia."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1079
translate spanish vfn80_check_19c463eb:

    # "You'd stare at her while she was getting dressed, much like you're doing now."
    "La mirabas fijamente mientras se vestía, como lo haces ahora."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1080
translate spanish vfn80_check_015e11c2:

    # Na "[persistent.player_name]... you're so quiet. Are you getting an eyeful...?"
    Na "[persistent.player_name]... estás muy callado. ¿Estás echando un vistazo...?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1081
translate spanish vfn80_check_6b20e1f1:

