    "... dice en su tono más sensual hasta ahora."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1082
translate spanish vfn80_check_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1083
translate spanish vfn80_check_00fb0a5e:

    # Na "Hm... no answer is also an answer, I guess. {i}*giggles*"
    Na "Hm... ninguna respuesta también es una respuesta, supongo. {i}*risitas*"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1089
translate spanish vfn99_f55739e7:

    # Na "Alright; done!"
    Na "Muy bien; ¡hecho!"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1090
translate spanish vfn99_49220156:

    # Na "I bet you remember this one."
    Na "Apuesto a que recuerdas esto."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1093
translate spanish vfn99_b01f9de2:

    # Na "Someone else wore it before me..."
    Na "Otra persona lo llevó antes que yo..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1094
translate spanish vfn99_aa1d1a28:

    # Na "...and I'm told that you were there to see it."
    Na "... y me dicen que tú estabas allí para verlo."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1097
translate spanish vfn99_d9853cc3:

    # Z "This is..."
    Z "Esto es..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1100
translate spanish vfn99_afd2da01:

    # Z "...your mother's..."
    Z "... de tu madre... ."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1101
translate spanish vfn99_33d21c4a:

    # Z "Turn around, kid."
    Z "Date la vuelta, niña."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1104
translate spanish vfn99_b805aaeb:

    # "She turns around, facing you with a proud and confident look."
    "Se da la vuelta y te mira con orgullo y confianza."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1105
translate spanish vfn99_1bc94fec:

    # "As a flash of recognition travels across your face, you realise that Nadia was intentionally trying to get a reaction from you. "
    "Cuando un destello de reconocimiento recorre tu rostro, te das cuenta de que Nadia intentaba intencionadamente obtener una reacción de ti."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1106
translate spanish vfn99_68f9b185:

    # "She knew what she was doing, as the dress you haven't seen in a few decades brings many memories rushing back."
    "Sabía lo que hacía, pues el vestido que no has visto en varias décadas te trae muchos recuerdos."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1109
translate spanish vfn99_31eba5ff:

    # "...Rabiah's old dress, the one she wore when you both were still in your teenage years, now worn by her daughter."
    "... El viejo vestido de Rabiah, el que llevaba cuando ambos estabais aún en la adolescencia, ahora lo llevaba su hija."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1110
translate spanish vfn99_7de2c45f:

    # "And it fits her perfectly."
    "Y a ella le quedaba perfecto."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1111
translate spanish vfn99_dd2b53c4:

    # Na "{i}*giggles*{/i} You're supposed to say something, about now..."
    Na "{i}*risitas*{/i} Se supone que debes decir algo, más o menos ahora..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1112
translate spanish vfn99_1509bd0e:

    # Z "Yeah. Hold still for a moment..."
    Z "Sí. Quédate quieta un momento..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1115
translate spanish vfn99_74ac79a3:

    # Z "I have not seen that dress in a long, long time."
    Z "Hacía mucho, mucho tiempo que no veía ese vestido."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1116
translate spanish vfn99_40fc3110:

    # Na "No wonder... mom has gained so much weight, I think her ass alone would rip this dress in two. {i}*laughs*"
    Na "No me extraña... mamá ha engordado tanto, que creo que sólo su culo partiría este vestido en dos. {i}*risas*"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1119
translate spanish vfn99_734c6b64:

    # Na "So... ready to give me your opinion?"
    Na "Entonces... ¿listo para darme tu opinión?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1120
translate spanish vfn99_0d27e0c0:

    # Na "What should I do? What do you think of it?"
    Na "¿Qué debo hacer? ¿Qué te parece?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1124
translate spanish vfn99_722af838:

    # Na "Huh...?"
    Na "¿Eh...?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1125
translate spanish vfn99_ed4e376d:

    # Om "Nadia? [persistent.player_name]?"
    Om "¿Nadia? ¿[persistent.player_name]?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1128
translate spanish vfn99_83416087:

    # Om "Hey guys, I was looking for you-"
    Om "Ey chicos, os estaba buscando...."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1131
translate spanish vfn99_6d84547d:

    # Om "N-Nadia! What are you wearing? This isn't really appropriate!"
    Om "¡N-Nadia! ¿Qué llevas puesto? ¡Eso no es muy apropiado!"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1134
translate spanish vfn99_93a975a0:

    # Na "It's... not even that revealing. I was just trying on some old outfits and needed uncle's opinion..."
    Na "Ni siquiera es tan... sugerente. Sólo me estaba probando algunos conjuntos viejos y necesitaba la opinión del tío..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1137
translate spanish vfn99_68cc6284:

    # Om "Where did you get this from, sweety? I will have to have a chat with the trader who sold you this!"
    Om "¿De dónde has sacado eso, cielo? ¡Tendré que hablar con el comerciante que te lo vendió!"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1138
translate spanish vfn99_5633ed37:

    # Om "What will people think if they see you in a dress like that? They'll think you're someone's concubine!"
    Om "¿Qué pensará la gente si te ve con un vestido así? ¡Pensarán que eres la concubina de alguien!"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1141
translate spanish vfn99_9bca8ad4:

    # Om "You know I love you, but you really should stop going out wearing such kind of clothes."
    Om "Sabes que te quiero, pero deberías dejar de salir con este tipo de ropa."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1142
translate spanish vfn99_35fc6ad4:

    # Om "I mean, this dress... look at your chest, and the straps... are you even wearing underwear?"
    Om "Quiero decir, este vestido... mira tu pecho, y los tirantes... ¿llevas siquiera ropa interior?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1143
translate spanish vfn99_810ad5ba:

    # "As you listen to Omar prattle on, you look at Nadia, stood there with the bored expression of someone about to walk away, you insert yourself in the conversation as delicately as you can."
    "Mientras escuchas a Omar parlotear, miras a Nadia, de pie con la expresión aburrida de alguien que está a punto de marcharse, y te introduces en la conversación tan delicadamente como puedes."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1144
translate spanish vfn99_877f9616:

    # Z "Look... uh... Omar."
    Z "Mira... eh... Omar."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1147
translate spanish vfn99_dc0e857d:

    # Z "This is actually her mother's dress, from when she was about Nadia's age. She wanted to show it to me, for old times sake."
    Z "En realidad es un vestido de su madre, de cuando ella tenía más o menos la edad de Nadia. Quería enseñármelo, por los viejos tiempos."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1148
translate spanish vfn99_e7d3bdf5:

    # Z "You know, she was just trying on some outfits. Just having a bit of fun."
    Z "Sólo se estaba probando algunos vestidos. Simplemente se divertía un poco."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1149
translate spanish vfn99_9af4c2f1:

    # Z "Look, I have an idea."
    Z "Mira, tengo una idea."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1152
translate spanish vfn99_ae4699ed:

    # Z "Why don't you join us. She wanted my opinion, now we can both give her some sensible advice."
    Z "¿Por qué no te unes a nosotros? Quería mi opinión, ahora los dos podemos darle algún consejo sensato."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1153
translate spanish vfn99_352b1d3a:

    # Om "I guess I could, if you'd... like me to?"
    Om "Supongo que podría, si... ¿quieres que lo haga?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1156
translate spanish vfn99_52a3defd:

    # "You push the chair towards him. He sits down."
    "Le empujas la silla... Y él se sienta."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1159
translate spanish vfn99_8e4a069c:

    # Z "See Nadia? Now you have two men helping you."
    Z "¿Lo ves Nadia? Ahora tienes a dos hombres ayudándote."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1162
translate spanish vfn99_6501cb2b:

    # Na "Okay then, I guess we can continue?"
    Na "Vale, supongo que ¿podemos continuar?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1163
translate spanish vfn99_39d63b46:

    # "Nadia grins mischievously. You're not entirely certain what you have set in motion, but she seems to have a plan."
    "Nadia sonríe con picardía. No está del todo segura de lo que ha puesto en marcha, pero parece tener un plan."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1164
translate spanish vfn99_066b7863:

    # Na "Take a look again, guys. Tell me what you think, and yes, I am wearing undies"
    Na "Volved a echar un vistazo, chicos. Decidme qué os parece, y sí, llevo ropa interior."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1167
translate spanish vfn99_900f0148:

    # Z "Hm..."
    Z "Hm..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1168
translate spanish vfn99_7b7307bc:

    # Na "And Omar, don't judge before you look closer, please?"
    Na "Y Omar, no juzgues antes de mirar más de cerca, ¿por favor?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1169
translate spanish vfn99_5698076b:

    # Na "I promise you I'd never wear this outside."
    Na "Te prometo que nunca me pondría esto fuera."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1170
translate spanish vfn99_374eea1a:

    # Om "Okay... I can try, sweetie."
    Om "Vale... Puedo intentarlo, cariño."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1171
translate spanish vfn99_a3d3483f:

    # Na "Uncle, you start first. What do you think?"
    Na "Tío, empieza tú primero. ¿Qué te parece?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1176
translate spanish vfn99_ecb11821:

    # Z "It's cute and suits you well."
    Z "Es mono y te sienta bien."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1177
translate spanish vfn99_1959f032:

    # Z "Just like when your mom wore it, in her days."
    Z "Igual que cuando lo llevaba tu madre, en sus tiempos."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1178
translate spanish vfn99_3d7e5905:

    # Om "My wife really was different back then. If she wore this now..."
    Om "Mi mujer era realmente diferente entonces. Si ella llevara eso ahora..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1179
translate spanish vfn99_77bfa0fe:

    # Z "She was, indeed, and, in my opinion, that's not such a bad thing as you make it sound."
    Z "Lo era, en efecto, y, en mi opinión, eso no es tan malo como lo haces parecer."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1180
translate spanish vfn99_0d414fbf:

    # Z "Today, Zetan girls her age are used to wearing much more revealing things."
    Z "Hoy en día, las chicas zetanas de su edad están acostumbradas a llevar cosas mucho más atrevidas."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1183
translate spanish vfn99_50366417:

    # Om "I guess you're right about that... but I am still not a fan, to be honest. Sorry, sweetie."
    Om "Supongo que en eso tienes razón... pero sigo sin ser fan, la verdad. Lo siento, cariño."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1184
translate spanish vfn99_4d13fb69:

    # Na "Yeah, whatever."
    Na "Sí, como quieras."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1190
translate spanish vfn99_f446c855:

    # Z "Just like when your mother wore it, it shows just the right amount of skin to make any red-blooded man want to look closer."
    Z "Igual que cuando lo llevaba tu madre, muestra la cantidad justa de piel para que cualquier hombre de sangre roja quiera mirar más de cerca."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1191
translate spanish vfn99_7d40f17d:

    # Z "Just the right side of provocative without being openly slutty."
    Z "El lado justo de la provocación sin ser abiertamente obsceno."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1194
translate spanish vfn99_2b9f50f2:

    # Om "[persistent.player_name]! How can you say that?! No, this is too much! Nadia, take it off!"
    Om "¡[persistent.player_name]! ¿Cómo puedes decir eso? No, ¡esto es demasiado! Nadia, ¡quítatelo!"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1195
translate spanish vfn99_62a445ea:

    # Z "I believe, Omar, that getting her to take it off is entirely the purpose of this dress, but we're not supposed to say that."
    Z "Creo, Omar, que conseguir que se lo quite es totalmente el propósito de ese vestido, pero se supone que no debemos decirlo."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1196
translate spanish vfn99_d0e15d49:

    # Om "I didn't mean..."
    Om "No pretendía..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1197
translate spanish vfn99_92c17c2b:

    # Z "I know, I know... don't mind me."
    Z "Lo sé, lo sé... no me hagas caso."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1200
translate spanish vfn99_e882a2e0:

    # Na "Mmmmh...Anyway, point taken."
    Na "Mmmmh... En fin, entendido."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1205
translate spanish vfn99_54e0185a:

    # "As you look at Nadia, a sense of unease takes you for a few seconds. Then you shake your head to clear your mind and reply to her."
    "Cuando miras a Nadia, una sensación de inquietud te invade durante unos segundos. Luego sacudes la cabeza para despejarte y le respondes."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1206
translate spanish vfn99_2ccb4508:

    # Z "I like the dress, don't get me wrong, but... it's weird seeing you wear it. To me this dress inevitably reminds me of your mother."
    Z "Me gusta el vestido, no me malinterpretes, pero... es raro verte con él puesto. A mí ese vestido me recuerda inevitablemente a tu madre."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1207
translate spanish vfn99_d30ab485:

    # Z "I also think the colours suited her better than they work for you."
    Z "También creo que los colores le sentaban mejor a ella que a ti."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1210
translate spanish vfn99_f7ff51bb:

    # Na "Everybody is a critic..."
    Na "Todo el mundo es crítico..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1211
translate spanish vfn99_30a393d8:

    # Z "You specifically asked me in here for that, didn't you?"
    Z "Me has invitado expresamente para esto, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1214
translate spanish vfn99_11d76763:

    # Na "Yes... Sure, {i}that's{/i} what I asked you in the room for."
    Na "Sí... Claro, {i}para eso{/i} te pedí que entraras en la habitación."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1215
translate spanish vfn99_0c6078b7:

    # Om "Well, {i}I{/i} think... "
    Om "Bueno, {i}yo{/i} creo..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1216
translate spanish vfn99_38122022:

    # Na "Save it... I am taking it off."
    Na "Ahórratelo... ya me lo estoy quitando."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1222
translate spanish vfn118_fea90f09:

    # Na "I will try something different on now. Could you close your eyes as I change?"
    Na "Ahora probaré algo diferente. ¿Podríais cerrar los ojos mientras me cambio?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1223
translate spanish vfn118_db03bf64:

    # Na "You wouldn't want to embarrass me, after all..."
    Na "No querríais avergonzarme, después de todo..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1224
translate spanish vfn118_482e3bdd:

    # "As the dress starts peeling off, held aloft by her hands cupping her breasts, Nadia looks at you directly, with hungry eyes tinted by mischievousness..."
    "Mientras el vestido comienza a desprenderse, sostenido por sus manos que le cubren los pechos, Nadia te mira directamente, con ojos hambrientos teñidos de picardía..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1227
translate spanish vfn118_9695080c:

    # Om "Oh, yes, of course!"
    Om "Oh, sí, ¡por supuesto!"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1228
translate spanish vfn118_a6f977af:

    # Om "Let me know when you're done. I won't look."
    Om "Avísame cuando hayas terminado. No miraré."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1229
translate spanish vfn118_f0434c5b:

    # Na "Thank you, Omar."
    Na "Gracias, Omar."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1232
translate spanish vfn118_5652e088:

    # Na "Okay... I'm undressed. Please keep your eyes closed..."
    Na "Vale... Ya me he desnudado. Por favor, mantener los ojos cerrados..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1233
translate spanish vfn118_7f3de46e:

    # "She gazes at you with a sly expression..."
    "Ella te mira con expresión socarrona..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1237
translate spanish vfn118_e3aedcc7:

    # Z "Damn..."
    Z "Joder..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1238
translate spanish vfn118_48325abb:

    # Om "Damn? Why damn? What's wrong?"
    Om "¿Maldita sea? ¿Por qué maldices? ¿Qué pasa?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1239
translate spanish vfn118_3021afe3:

    # Z "Uh, nothing..."
    Z "Uh, nada..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1242
translate spanish vfn118_e952fdee:

    # Z "...You better hurry up, Nadia. I don't like to wait."
    Z "... Será mejor que te des prisa, Nadia. No me gusta esperar."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1243
translate spanish vfn118_3500ad5a:

    # Na "Yeah... I am doing my best."
    Na "Sí... Hago lo que puedo."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1246
translate spanish vfn118_b75b7e77:

    # Zt "The way she just stands there..."
    Zt "La forma en que permanece ahí de pie..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1247
translate spanish vfn118_bfabd904:

    # Zt "Slim, athletic and with such a wild head of hair... if sirens were real, she could be one of them."
    Zt "Delgada, atlética y con una melena tan salvaje... si las sirenas fueran reales, ella podría ser una de ellas."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1250
translate spanish vfn118_8706ca71:

    # Zt "Her ass... I didn't think she could improve on her mother's best features, but here we are."
    Zt "Su culo... No creía que pudiera mejorar los mejores rasgos de su madre, pero aquí estamos."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1251
translate spanish vfn118_bcd9d589:

    # Z "You really like to take your time, huh..."
    Z "Realmente te gusta tomarte tu tiempo, eh..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1252
translate spanish vfn118_bbe9dbc3:

    # Na "Yeah. Sorry, uncle."
    Na "Sí. Lo siento, tío."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1256
