    Z "¿Nadia? Soy yo."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1599
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_1c36a985:

    # Na "Uncle? Come in..."
    Na "¿Tío? Pasa..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1603
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_36407e57:

    # Z "So this is your room. Interesting..."
    Z "Esta es tu habitación. Interesante..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1606
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_dcb8147a:

    # Na "Heyy, yeps, it's my personal space."
    Na "Eyyy, sip, es mi espacio personal."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1607
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_23f2dd46:

    # Na "The twins are in the next room. I guess Mother will have to feed the little goblins again, later tonight."
    Na "Los gemelos están en la habitación de al lado. Supongo que mamá tendrá que volver a alimentar a los pequeños duendes, esta misma noche."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1608
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_c16673f1:

    # Na "I didn't know babies pooped that much."
    Na "No sabía que los bebés hicieran tanta caca."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1611
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_ac6c2e75:

    # Na "How's the evening going? Is dinner ready yet?"
    Na "¿Cómo va la noche? ¿Ya está lista la cena?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1612
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_3a582d3e:

    # Z "Not yet, no. I'm just here to see how you're doing..."
    Z "Todavía no. Sólo estoy aquí para ver cómo te va..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1615
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_a90d3e99:

    # Na "Getting tired of Omar's stories, huh?"
    Na "Te estás cansando de las historias de Omar, ¿eh?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1620
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_47ea0f85:

    # Z "You can say that out loud."
    Z "Puedes decirlo en voz alta."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1621
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_106c0275:

    # Z "The way he's blabbering on, you'd think he doesn't get to talk much, with either you or your mother."
    Z "Por la forma en que parlotea, se diría que no habla mucho, ni contigo ni con tu madre."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1624
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_0fafab55:

    # "You move towards the bed..."
    "Te diriges hacia la cama..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1627
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_ceeb4b6b:

    # Na "I know. He doesn't."
    Na "Lo sé. El no lo hace."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1628
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_3a4238f2:

    # Na "I try to avoid him, to be honest."
    Na "Intento evitarlo, para ser sincera."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1634
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_2990b5f2:

    # Z "Nice dress, are you going to become a priestess now?"
    Z "Bonito vestido, ¿vas a convertirte en sacerdotisa ahora?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1637
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_cf1425dd:

    # Na "Oh, this?"
    Na "Oh, ¿esto?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1638
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_d1149432:

    # Na "{i}*giggles*{/i} No, I don't think I would be a good fit for that role."
    Na "{i}*risas*{/i} No, no creo que encaje bien en ese papel."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1639
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_1e372590:

    # Na "I just saw it at the market and it looked comfortable, so I bought it."
    Na "Lo vi en el mercado y me pareció cómodo, así que lo compré."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1642
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_f4365e9a:

    # Na "You think people would confuse me for one of them, if they saw me with this?"
    Na "¿Crees que la gente me confundiría con una de ellas, si me vieran con esto?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1643
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_67014e6d:

    # Z "Why wouldn't they? Sometimes the looks do make the woman, and this is very close to their traditional garb."
    Z "¿Por qué no? A veces las apariencias hacen a la mujer, y esto se parece mucho a su vestimenta tradicional."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1644
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_2b5c0464:

    # Na "Fair point, I guess..."
    Na "Es justo, supongo..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1647
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_c4a4a88b:

    # Na "I think I'll keep it, anyway."
    Na "De todas formas, creo que me lo quedaré."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1650
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_0fafab55_1:

    # "You move towards the bed..."
    "Te diriges hacia la cama..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1653
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_bbffbc81:

    # Na "{i}*sigh*"
    Na "{i}*suspiro*{/i}"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1656
translate spanish nadia_convi_1_0b41d7cd:

    # Z "What's the problem?"
    Z "¿Cuál es el problema?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1660
translate spanish vfn14_cf8cb8f2:

    # Na "Sorry for taking off last time. I'm not like that usually."
    Na "Siento haberme ido la última vez. No suelo ser así."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1661
translate spanish vfn14_5a5c2472:

    # Na "It's just that those comments made me uncomfortable."
    Na "Es sólo que esos comentarios me incomodaron."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1664
translate spanish vfn14_77162836:

    # Na "It's enough that he exhausts mom already. Me? I want him to back off."
    Na "Ya es suficiente con que agote a mamá. ¿Yo? Quiero que se retire."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1667
translate spanish vfn14_36c3bc48:

    # Z "Because he expects you to do chores, too?"
    Z "¿Porque también espera que hagas tareas?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1670
translate spanish vfn14_5159617d:

    # Na "I would do them, but it's how he goes about it that bugs me. It's not like he couldn't afford to buy some help, servants..."
    Na "Yo las haría, pero lo que me molesta es cómo lo hace. No es que no pueda permitirse comprar ayuda, criados..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1671
translate spanish vfn14_9a68ef30:

    # Na "But I guess he's too much of a cheapskate. So he's all manipulative towards mom and me, instead of flat out asking us to do things..."
    Na "Pero supongo que es demasiado tacaño. Por eso es tan manipulador con mamá y conmigo, en vez de pedirnos directamente que hagamos cosas..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1672
translate spanish vfn14_bccb0bfe:

    # Na "He just tries to guilt us into things..."
    Na "Sólo intenta hacernos sentir culpables..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1675
translate spanish vfn14_d4fe7bdd:

    # "She comes closer..."
    "Se acerca..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1678
translate spanish vfn14_eae7c7a1:

    # Na "Anyway, enough about him."
    Na "En fin, basta de hablar de él."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1679
translate spanish vfn14_e011fd7c:

    # Na "Do you know what I always wondered?"
    Na "¿Sabes lo que siempre me he preguntado?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1682
translate spanish vfn14_9d1986a3:

    # Z "What would that be?"
    Z "¿El qué?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1685
translate spanish vfn14_9d6dfd7f:

    # "She climbs on the bed..."
    "Ella se sube a la cama..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1689
translate spanish vfn14_28bb911d:

    # Na "Now that I know first hand why they liked you..."
    Na "Ahora que sé de primera mano por qué les gustabas..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1690
translate spanish vfn14_94578a14:

    # Na "I always wondered why you chose auntie over my mother."
    Na "Siempre me he preguntado por qué elegiste a la tía y no a mi madre."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1691
translate spanish vfn14_4e47e875:

    # Na "I know she wasn't as stuck up as she is now, so what was it?"
    Na "Sé que no era tan presumida como ahora, así que ¿qué fue?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1698
translate spanish vfn14_b28ea737:

    # Z "You want to hear the full story, huh?"
    Z "¿Quieres oír la historia completa?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1702
translate spanish vfn14_f9fea624:

    # Na "Yes."
    Na "Sí."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1706
translate spanish vfn14_02280d64:

    # Na "Will you tell me what happened?"
    Na "¿Me vas a contar qué pasó?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1710
translate spanish vfn14_9a2d63f4:

    # Z "Well, I guess we should start at the very beginning."
    Z "Supongo que deberíamos empezar por el principio."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1711
translate spanish vfn14_33f5154e:

    # Z "I first met your aunt on a bright summer day..."
    Z "Conocí a tu tía un brillante día de verano..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1715
translate spanish vfn14_496f0a8f:

    # Z "Your mother and I had been together for a few months, and I had never really seen her sister until that point."
    Z "Tu madre y yo llevábamos juntos unos meses, y yo nunca había visto a su hermana hasta ese momento."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1719
translate spanish vfn14_c0583f0c:

    # Z "I guess there just hadn't been an occasion for it."
    Z "Supongo que no había habido ocasión para ello."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1720
translate spanish vfn14_3f12ce95:

    # Z "I was in the middle of my training to become a Zetan Stalker, and after my lessons and training, I would meet up with your mother."
    Z "Estaba en medio de mi entrenamiento para convertirme en un acechador zetano, y después de mis lecciones y entrenamiento, me reuniría con tu madre."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1723
translate spanish vfn14_68b03b08:

    # Z "That day however was a little different."
    Z "Ese día, sin embargo, era un poco diferente."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1724
translate spanish vfn14_04cf4230:

    # Z "[W]'s birthday had been just a few days prior, and since she had been a bit sheltered until then, she didn't have a great many friends to celebrate with."
    Z "El cumpleaños de [W] había sido sólo unos días antes, y como hasta entonces había estado un poco protegida, no tenía muchos amigos con los que celebrarlo."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1725
translate spanish vfn14_0be1a233:

    # Z "So Rabiah had kept her company and asked me to let her tag along, so she wouldn't be on her own."
    Z "Así que Rabiah le hizo compañía y me pidió que la dejara acompañarla, para que no estuviera sola."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1728
translate spanish vfn14_4dd41d8d:

    # Z "I agreed, of course, and eventually we met at one of our usual spots, just outside the city."
    Z "Estuve de acuerdo, por supuesto, y al final quedamos en uno de nuestros lugares habituales, a las afueras de la ciudad."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1729
translate spanish vfn14_b363322e:

    # Z "I found them waiting for me, together, talking amongst themselves."
    Z "Las encontré esperándome, juntas, hablando entre ellas."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1730
translate spanish vfn14_1680c5e8:

    # Z "[W] eventually, much later, told me what they talked about..."
    Z "[W] con el tiempo, mucho más tarde, me contó lo que hablaron..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1734
translate spanish vfn14_d4da2ac5:

    # Yra "I don't know, [W]... I really like him, but..."
    Yra "No sé, [W]... me gusta mucho, pero..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1735
translate spanish vfn14_30868167:

    # Yra "I'm not sure if this Stalker thing is the best idea."
    Yra "No estoy segura de que esto del Acechador sea la mejor idea."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1736
translate spanish vfn14_ddfb1547:

    # Yra "Once he starts going on missions or looking for treasures... Who knows how long he will be gone..."
    Yra "Una vez que empiece a ir a misiones o a buscar tesoros... quién sabe cuánto tiempo estará fuera..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1739
translate spanish vfn14_dc7c2b9d:

    # Yra "And don't get me started on how dangerous it is. He could die any time he goes out there."
    Yra "Y no me hagas hablar de lo peligrosa que es. Puede morir en cualquier momento que salga ahí fuera."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1742
translate spanish vfn14_05828d0e:

    # Yw "I don't know... from what you tell me, he really wants to do this, and he's a good student."
    Yw "No sé... por lo que me cuentas, realmente quiere hacer esto, y es un buen estudiante."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1745
translate spanish vfn14_76419b41:

    # Yra "I know. But there are other ways for a man to earn gold, you know what I mean?"
    Yra "Lo sé. Pero hay otras formas de que un hombre gane oro, ¿me entiendes?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1746
translate spanish vfn14_29bccac9:

    # Yra "He could become a Queen's guard, do his shift and come home. They are well provided for."
    Yra "Podría convertirse en guardia de la Reina, hacer su turno y volver a casa. Están bien provistos."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1747
translate spanish vfn14_89c74bde:

    # Yw "..."
    Yw "..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1750
translate spanish vfn14_e21ffe8e:

    # Na "So my mom never liked that you became a Stalker?"
    Na "¿Así que a mi madre nunca le gustó que te convirtieras en Acechador?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1751
translate spanish vfn14_6e2d6e4d:

    # Z "I don't think she disliked it as a concept. But she was always impatient."
    Z "No creo que le disgustara como concepto. Pero siempre se mostró impaciente."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1752
translate spanish vfn14_9d349d2e:

    # Z "She didn't like that I would be gone, potentially for days at a time."
    Z "No le gustaba que me fuera, posiblemente durante días."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1753
translate spanish vfn14_94b1064e:

    # Z "Anyway, where was I..."
    Z "De todos modos, ¿dónde estaba yo..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1754
translate spanish vfn14_be8803fb:

    # Yz "Rabiah? Are you here?"
    Yz "¿Rabiah? ¿Estás aquí?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1755
translate spanish vfn14_5a92ed4a:

    # Yra "We're here, sweetie!"
    Yra "¡Estamos aquí, cariño!"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1758
translate spanish vfn14_72257f29:

    # Yra "Look who finally made it..."
    Yra "Mira quién ha llegado por fin..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1759
translate spanish vfn14_8106a74b:

    # Yz "I came as fast as I could. [Zo] never lets me leave on time."
    Yz "He venido tan rápido como he podido. [Zo] nunca me deja salir a tiempo."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1762
translate spanish vfn14_94b57e1b:

    # Yra "Have you thought of everything?"
    Yra "¿Has pensado en todo?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1765
translate spanish vfn14_1e94d324:

    # Yz "Of course, why would I forget?"
    Yz "Por supuesto, ¿por qué iba a olvidarlo?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1768
translate spanish vfn14_7e2f7278:

    # Yz "Come here."
    Yz "Ven aquí."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1771
translate spanish vfn14_7ee49b4b:

    # Yra "{i}*kissing*"
    Yra "{i}*beso*{/i}"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1772
translate spanish vfn14_aef006a5:

    # Yz "It's good to see you."
    Yz "Me alegro de verte."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1776
translate spanish vfn14_11a9cb25:

    # Yz "Now greet me properly."
    Yz "Ahora salúdame como es debido."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1779
translate spanish vfn14_7ee49b4b_1:

    # Yra "{i}*kissing*"
    Yra "{i}*beso*{/i}"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1782
translate spanish vfn14_9d92cca6:

    # Yra "Mhm..."
    Yra "Mhm..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1785
translate spanish vfn14_525ac8fd:

    # Yz "You look great in this dress."
    Yz "Te queda muy bien este vestido."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1786
translate spanish vfn14_415af584:

    # Yra "Well thank you... I can feel that you like it. {i}*giggles*"
    Yra "Bueno, gracias... Puedo sentir que te gusta. {i}*risas*"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1787
translate spanish vfn14_322ca22a:

    # Na "I could never imagine mom saying that nowadays."
    Na "Nunca podría imaginarme a mamá diciendo eso hoy en día."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1788
translate spanish vfn14_de30b410:

    # Na "Did she look different, too?"
    Na "¿Ella también se veía diferente?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1789
translate spanish vfn14_c5745137:

    # Z "She did indeed. She had a fine figure, slender... an amazing body."
    Z "En efecto, lo hizo. Tenía una figura fina, esbelta... un cuerpo increíble."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1792
translate spanish vfn14_200a7064:

    # Z "And that ass... man I considered myself a lucky guy, with good reason."
    Z "Y ese culo... tío me consideraba un tipo con suerte, con razón."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1795
translate spanish vfn14_89c74bde_1:

    # Yw "..."
    Yw "..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1799
translate spanish vfn14_349f0f57:

    # Na "So..."
    Na "Así que..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1802
translate spanish vfn14_6c8be071:

    # Na "What do you think..."
    Na "¿Qué piensas..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1805
translate spanish vfn14_91edb8c7:

    # Na "Do I take after my mom or not...?"
    Na "... me parezco a mi madre o no...?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:1808
