translate spanish visit_family_4d389e38:

    # Z "Deal."
    Z "Trato hecho."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:2990
translate spanish visit_family_0252cf2b:

    # "You both get ready and eventually head out. After the usual 30 minute walk you arrive in Zeta."
    "Los dos os preparáis y finalmente salís. Tras el habitual paseo de 30 minutos, llegáis a Zeta."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:2991
translate spanish visit_family_f97a6427:

    # "From that point, it's only a few more minutes before you reach the residential area of the city."
    "Desde ese punto, sólo faltan unos minutos para llegar a la zona residencial de la ciudad."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:2992
translate spanish visit_family_cbdd60b1:

    # "Eventually..."
    "Finalmente..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:2996
translate spanish visit_family_6502350f:

    # Om "Nice to see you both! Thank you for visiting our little home!"
    Om "¡Me alegro de veros! ¡Gracias por visitar nuestro pequeño hogar!"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:2999
translate spanish visit_family_550a791a:

    # Om "It's great that we finally get to have a nice little family gathering."
    Om "Es estupendo que por fin podamos celebrar una pequeña reunión familiar."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3000
translate spanish visit_family_9786841e:

    # Om "Nadia isn't here yet, she's probably in her room, still dressing up. You know how it is, haha."
    Om "Nadia aún no está aquí, probablemente esté en su habitación, todavía vistiéndose. Ya sabéis cómo es, jajaja."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3003
translate spanish visit_family_cf3c0e49:

    # Om "Talking about dressing up, [persistent.player_name], your wife looks fantastic, as always."
    Om "Hablando de vestirse, [persistent.player_name], tu mujer está fantástica, como siempre."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3004
translate spanish visit_family_a4d02ed6:

    # Om "Really nice dress too!"
    Om "¡Realmente es un vestido muy bonito!"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3007
translate spanish visit_family_7569bc6b:

    # W "Thanks, Omar..."
    W "Gracias, Omar..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3012
translate spanish visit_family_7f86043d:

    # Z "She knows what to wear to make a head turn for sure, she always did."
    Z "Ella sabe qué ponerse para hacer girar la cabeza sin duda, siempre lo ha hecho."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3015
translate spanish visit_family_8480ba57:

    # Om "I don't disagree, haha. That's the look of a confident woman!"
    Om "No estoy en desacuerdo, jajaja. ¡Esa es la mirada de una mujer segura de sí misma!"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3016
translate spanish visit_family_65068e72:

    # Om "Reminds me a bit of my stepdaughter, if you ask me. This liberal and upfront atti-"
    Om "En mi opinión, me recuerda un poco a mi hijastra. Esa actitud liberal y franca-"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3019
translate spanish visit_family_81cd716f:

    # Ra "Husband, why don't you invite our guests to make themselves at home?"
    Ra "Marido, ¿por qué no invitas a nuestros invitados a sentirse como en casa?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3020
translate spanish visit_family_082f64cb:

    # Ra "After walking all the way here, I'm sure they will want to take a seat..."
    Ra "Después de caminar hasta aquí, seguro que querrán sentarse..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3023
translate spanish visit_family_ef0eeef2:

    # Om "O-of course, Rabiah. [W], [persistent.player_name], follow me please."
    Om "Por supuesto, Rabiah. [W], [persistent.player_name], seguirme por favor."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3027
translate spanish visit_family_0d667b3a:

    # Om "So, I'm sure you're tired of walking."
    Om "Estoy seguro de que estáis cansados de caminar."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3030
translate spanish visit_family_425c7792:

    # Om "Follow me, we have prepared some refreshments too."
    Om "Seguirme, también hemos preparado unos refrescos."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3036
translate spanish vf9_225d82ee:

    # Om "Please, take a seat. I'm sure we have many stories to share."
    Om "Por favor, tomad asiento. Seguro que tenemos muchas historias que compartir."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3037
translate spanish vf9_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3038
translate spanish vf9_e0f8fc3a:

    # Z "Don't mind me, but the table in between..."
    Z "No me hagas caso, pero la mesa de en medio..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3039
translate spanish vf9_15592845:

    # Om "Yes? What about it?"
    Om "¿Sí? ¿Qué pasa con ella?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3042
translate spanish vf9_43b470f4:

    # Z "I'm sure you don't mind if I move it away, right?"
    Z "Seguro que no te importa que la aparte, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3043
translate spanish vf9_768e5e8f:

    # Z "I would like to sit next to my wife."
    Z "Me gustaría sentarme junto a mi mujer."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3046
translate spanish vf9_9f15cce9:

    # Om "Heh, sure. I didn't think about that, I guess."
    Om "Claro. Supongo que no había pensado en eso."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3047
translate spanish vf9_19c07132:

    # Om "Make yourselves at home!"
    Om "¡Sentiros como en casa!"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3050
translate spanish vf9_94368a74:

    # Z "I appreciate it."
    Z "Lo aprecio."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3051
translate spanish vf9_df0fec09:

    # Zt "...and the water. Who needs beer after all..."
    Zt "... y el agua. Quién necesita cerveza después de todo..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3054
translate spanish vf9_7087dde2:

    # "You and [W] sit down..."
    "Tú y [W] os sentáis..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3057
translate spanish vf9_3703002d:

    # Z "So Omar, I'm curious..."
    Z "Así que Omar, tengo curiosidad..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3060
translate spanish vf9_ca866480:

    # Z "How has business been these years, and why decide to move to Zeta after all this time?"
    Z "¿Cómo ha ido el negocio estos años, y por qué decidiste trasladarte a Zeta después de todo este tiempo?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3063
translate spanish vf9_5312e721:

    # Om "Business could not go better."
    Om "El negocio no podría ir mejor."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3064
translate spanish vf9_6466b974:

    # Om "I have managed to gain exclusive rights to certain essential goods and..."
    Om "He conseguido obtener los derechos exclusivos de ciertos bienes esenciales y..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3065
translate spanish vf9_5109cc72:

    # "He goes on..."
    "Y continúa..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3066
translate spanish vf9_5100ab1f:

    # Om "I have been able to basically neutralise the competition by..."
    Om "He sido capaz de neutralizar básicamente a la competencia..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3067
translate spanish vf9_e0a1c51c:

    # "He keeps going on..."
    "Y continúa..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3068
translate spanish vf9_e121fc09:

    # Om "It was a hard fought battle, but finally, if you want to buy a lentil or a date, now you must..."
    Om "Ha sido una dura batalla, pero finalmente, si quieres comprar una lenteja o un dátil, ahora debes..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3071
translate spanish vf9_687331dd:

    # Om "Oh, and chickpeas...did I tell you how I cornered the market on..."
    Om "Ah, y los garbanzos... ¿te he contado cómo he acaparado el mercado de..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3072
translate spanish vf9_e31fac2a:

    # "...and going..."
    "... y sigue..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3073
translate spanish vf9_5bd2353c:

    # Om "Old Werkas thought he was crafty but..."
    Om "El viejo Werkas se creía astuto, pero..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3074
translate spanish vf9_a1366971:

    # "...you've lost track of time..."
    "... perdió la noción del tiempo..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3075
translate spanish vf9_f1df3c88:

    # Om "So you could say I had outgrown the village. I mean, I was always the most prominent merchant there, but I needed a new challenge."
    Om "Así que se puede decir que se me quedó pequeña la aldea. Siempre fui el mercader más destacado de allí, pero necesitaba un nuevo reto."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3078
translate spanish vf9_3ab8be5a:

    # Om "Moving here, back to where Rabiah came from, seemed the logical next step."
    Om "Trasladarme aquí, de vuelta al lugar de origen de Rabiah, parecía el siguiente paso lógico."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3079
translate spanish vf9_c7c43a1a:

    # Om "The merchants guilds here are not going to know what hit them when..."
    Om "Los gremios de mercaderes de aquí no van a saber qué les golpeó cuando..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3082
translate spanish vf9_4df6348e:

    # Ww "...does he ever stop?"
    Ww "... ¿se detendrá alguna vez?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3083
translate spanish vf9_5220e18e:

    # Zw "You tell me..."
    Zw "Dime tú..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3087
translate spanish vf9_4838604b:

    # Na "Mom? Omar? Are they here yet?"
    Na "¿Mamá? ¿Omar? ¿Ya están aquí?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3090
translate spanish vf9_fc12ae67:

    # Na "Really mom?"
    Na "¿De verdad mamá?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3093
translate spanish vf9_46abaf87:

    # Na "You could at least have told me that they arrived."
    Na "Al menos podrías haberme dicho que habían llegado."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3096
translate spanish vf9_f7b9a559:

    # "She walks up to all of you..."
    "Ella se acerca a todos vosotros..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3099
translate spanish vf9_d41f7558:

    # Na "Sorry auntie, I'm sure you know what a bad hair day is."
    Na "Lo siento tía, estoy segura de que sabes lo que es un mal día del pelo."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3102
translate spanish vf9_617e2b4c:

    # W "What are you saying, Nadia. You look great."
    W "Qué dices, Nadia. Estás muy bien."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3105
translate spanish vf9_c641503c:

    # Na "It's nice to see you again."
    Na "Me alegro de volver a verte."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3108
translate spanish vf9_60365b64:

    # "{i}*kissing*"
    "{i}*beso*{/i}"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3111
translate spanish vf9_ebe09ab7:

    # Om "Heh, I..."
    Om "Jejeje, yo..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3114
translate spanish vf9_8a5b4027:

    # Om "You didn't tell me that your sister and Nadia were..."
    Om "No me dijiste que tu hermana y Nadia eran..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3117
translate spanish vf9_b3d1ea1e:

    # Na "Urgh Omar, stop being weird, I was just greeting my aunt."
    Na "Argh Omar, deja de ser raro, sólo estaba saludando a mi tía."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3118
translate spanish vf9_2383ccd1:

    # Na "Seriously..."
    Na "En serio..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3121
translate spanish vf9_ceef7588:

    # Na "Anyway, don't mind him, [W]..."
    Na "En fin, no le hagas caso, [W]..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3124
translate spanish vf9_e0c70c31:

    # Na "Hey uncle! How's it going?"
    Na "¡Ey tío! ¿Cómo te va?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3125
translate spanish vf9_dfdf8faf:

    # Z "Can't complain, and you?"
    Z "No me puedo quejar, ¿y tú?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3128
translate spanish vf9_b74fda31:

    # Na "Not bad either."
    Na "Tampoco me va mal."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3129
translate spanish vf9_70cfd5ba:

    # Na "Mind if I sit next to you?"
    Na "¿Te importa si me siento a tu lado?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3132
translate spanish vf9_3af47f93:

    # Z "Not at all."
    Z "No, en absoluto."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3135
translate spanish vf9_a465e555:

    # "She takes a seat..."
    "Ella se sienta..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3138
translate spanish vf9_ae559ff3:

    # Na "I'm sure I interrupted you, Omar. Sorry about that."
    Na "Estoy segura de que te interrumpí, Omar. Lo siento por eso."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3141
translate spanish vf9_8a0d1c88:

    # Om "Oh, that's fine. I'm glad you're here, finally."
    Om "Oh, no pasa nada. Me alegro de que estés aquí, por fin."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3142
translate spanish vf9_4afd6df7:

    # Om "So, where was I..."
    Om "Así que, por dónde iba..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3143
translate spanish vf9_d63674f7:

    # "He keeps talking about the same topic..."
    "El sigue hablando del mismo tema..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3146
translate spanish vf9_f3dcd637:

    # "...for what seems like an eternity."
    "... durante lo que parece una eternidad."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3147
translate spanish vf9_fe5e69e3:

    # Zt "I regret asking..."
    Zt "Me arrepiento de haber preguntado..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3150
translate spanish vf9_94e104e1:

    # Zt "...but at least I'm in good company."
    Zt "... pero al menos estoy en buena compañía."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3153
translate spanish vf9_5ab3574d_1:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3156
translate spanish vf9_5cb9fc7e:

    # Zw "You look stunning. Omar is losing his mind over you."
    Zw "Estás impresionante. Omar está perdiendo la cabeza por ti."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3157
translate spanish vf9_5032e4fb:

    # Zw "He commented on you last time already."
    Zw "Ya hizo un comentario sobre ti la última vez."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3160
translate spanish vf9_46e9fd52:

    # Ww "As if his opinion could matter to me. Is he that insecure though?"
    Ww "Como si su opinión pudiera importarme. ¿Es tan inseguro?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3163
translate spanish vf9_7c6e9f87:

    # Ra "..."
    Ra "..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3164
translate spanish vf9_99e1119a:

    # "He keeps talking..."
    "El no para de hablar..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3167
translate spanish vf9_df2268df:

    # Om "Anyway, so then I went-"
    Om "En fin, entonces fui-"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3168
translate spanish vf9_c917b77c:

    # Ra "Husband..."
    Ra "Marido..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3171
translate spanish vf9_468c2d46:

    # Om "Yes, dear?"
    Om "¿Sí, querida?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3172
translate spanish vf9_e8dd325f:

    # Ra "I'm sure you don't mind if I head to the kitchen."
    Ra "Seguro que no te importa que me dirija a la cocina."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3173
translate spanish vf9_0637fb04:

    # Ra "Dinner needs to be prepared."
    Ra "Hay que preparar la cena."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3176
translate spanish vf9_35c3a41c:

    # Om "Oh, hah, of course. Feel free."
    Om "Por supuesto. Siéntete libre."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3179
translate spanish vf9_67a52203:

    # Om "Make sure to not salt the soup too much this time, hehe."
    Om "Asegúrate de no salar demasiado la sopa esta vez, jejeje."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3182
translate spanish vf9_e03b1081:

    # Om "Such a good wife, always thinking about her duties."
    Om "Qué buena esposa, siempre pensando en sus deberes."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3183
translate spanish vf9_f9c4457f:

    # Om "Maybe you want to help her out, Nadia?"
    Om "¿Quizás quieras ayudarla, Nadia?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3184
translate spanish vf9_0ac18966:

    # Om "It would not be wrong for you to help your parents out, don't you think?"
    Om "No estaría mal que ayudaras a tus padres, ¿no crees?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3187
translate spanish vf9_19b8484f:

    # Na "Hnnn, very funny Omar..."
    Na "Unnn, muy gracioso Omar..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3190
translate spanish vf9_be650adb:

    # Na "No. I don't think I will."
    Na "No. No creo que lo haga."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3193
translate spanish vf9_76360a30:

    # "She gets up..."
    "Se levanta..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3196
translate spanish vf9_e6d389aa:

    # Na "Aaand that's enough for me for today, I'm sorry but I've got to go."
    Na "Y ya está bien por hoy, lo siento pero me tengo que ir."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3199
translate spanish vf9_e2f073cd:

    # Na "It was nice listening to {i}you{/i} for a change..."
    Na "Ha sido agradable escucharte a {i}ti{/i} para variar..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3202
translate spanish vf9_1aa15994:

    # Om "Don't mind Nadia, she's always running about, lately."
    Om "No te preocupes por Nadia, últimamente siempre está corriendo de un lado a otro."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3205
translate spanish vf9_6433fd58:

    # Om "That leaves us three, I guess!"
    Om "Eso nos deja a nosotros tres, ¡supongo!"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3206
translate spanish vf9_bbffbc81:

    # Na "{i}*sigh*"
    Na "{i}*suspiro*{/i}"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3209
translate spanish vf9_048b96a4:

    # "Nadia briskly leaves the room."
    "Nadia sale enérgicamente de la habitación."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3211
translate spanish vf9_a14280e0:

    # "The conversation eventually shifts, and you find yourself looking around the room, while Omar is talking to [W]."
    "La conversación acaba cambiando, y te encuentras mirando alrededor de la habitación, mientras Omar está hablando con [W]."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3214
translate spanish vf9_fa775cb5:

    # Zt "It's no accident he left that chest open."
    Zt "No es casualidad que haya dejado el cofre abierto."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3215
translate spanish vf9_b9ef179c:

    # Zt "...The guy loves to show off whenever he can."
    Zt "... Al tipo le encanta presumir siempre que puede."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3216
translate spanish vf9_e2a5c6ce:

    # Zt "The way Nadia and Rabiah reacted to his remarks, there doesn't seem to be much harmony in this family."
    Zt "Por la forma en que Nadia y Rabiah reaccionaron a sus comentarios, no parece haber mucha armonía en esta familia."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3220
translate spanish vf9_0bf54150:

    # Zt "Poor [W]. Hanging in there so I can take a break."
    Zt "Pobre [W]. Aguantando para que yo pueda tomar un descanso."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3221
translate spanish vf9_dbb12256:

    # Zt "Let's hope the food will be good at least. I can't remember the last time Rabiah cooked for me."
    Zt "Esperemos que la comida sea buena al menos. No recuerdo la última vez que Rabiah cocinó para mí."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3228
translate spanish end_scene_rabiah_64afbb3b:

    # Ra "You can let everyone know dinner is ready. I'm done here."
    Ra "Puedes avisar a todos de que la cena está lista. Ya he terminado."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3231
translate spanish end_scene_rabiah_2382d616:

    # "You came together for dinner, spending most of it in awkward silence, and then went home..."
    "Os reunisteis para cenar, pasando la mayor parte de la cena en incómodo silencio, y luego os fuisteis a casa..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3234
translate spanish end_scene_rabiah_64afbb3b_1:

    # Ra "You can let everyone know dinner is ready. I'm done here."
    Ra "Puedes avisar a todos de que la cena está lista. Ya he terminado."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3237
translate spanish end_scene_rabiah_127b3fce:

    # Ra "You can go back to the living room, Omar. I am still preparing dinner."
    Ra "Puedes volver al salón, Omar. Todavía estoy preparando la cena."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3240
translate spanish end_scene_rabiah_42421d65:

    # "You head back to the living room. Omar follows soon after."
    "Te diriges de nuevo al salon. Omar te sigue poco después."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3246
translate spanish end_scene_nadia_ed4e376d:

    # Om "Nadia? [persistent.player_name]?"
    Om "¿Nadia? ¿[persistent.player_name]?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3251
translate spanish end_scene_nadia_ea33353c:

    # Na "What is it, Omar?"
    Na "¿Qué pasa, Omar?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3252
translate spanish end_scene_nadia_3a79ef36:

    # Om "Your mother wants to let you know that dinner is..."
    Om "Tu madre quiere que sepas que la cena está..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3255
translate spanish end_scene_nadia_b6c50247:

    # Om "Wait, what are you wearing!?"
    Om "Espera, ¿¡qué llevas puesto!?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3258
translate spanish end_scene_nadia_b15e42cd:

    # Na "{i}*sigh*{/i} I'm just showing my dress to uncle."
    Na "{i}*suspiro*{/i} Sólo le estoy enseñando mi vestido al tío."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3261
translate spanish end_scene_nadia_b1539a3a:

    # Na "I'm not wearing it outside, ok? Calm down, already!"
    Na "No me lo voy a poner fuera, ¿vale? ¡Cálmate ya!"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3262
translate spanish end_scene_nadia_98a49116:

    # Na "Give us a few minutes and we will join you."
    Na "Danos unos minutos y nos reuniremos con vosotros."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3265
translate spanish end_scene_nadia_225cfc9e:

    # Om "Okay honey."
    Om "De acuerdo, cariño."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3269
translate spanish end_scene_nadia_87dd7051:

    # Na "We can continue this next time, okay?"
    Na "Podemos continuar con esto la próxima vez, ¿vale?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3272
translate spanish end_scene_nadia_3f8a6cbc:

    # Z "Sure..."
    Z "Claro..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3273
translate spanish end_scene_nadia_29705fbb:

    # Z "I'm hungry, let's see what your mom prepared."
    Z "Tengo hambre, vamos a ver lo que ha preparado tu madre."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3280
translate spanish end_scene_nadia_44813d6f:

    # Z "Whoa, I think that was enough for today. The others are probably wondering where I am."
    Z "Guau, creo que ha sido suficiente por hoy. Los demás se estarán preguntando dónde estoy."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3281
translate spanish end_scene_nadia_beefc375:

    # Z "Let's continue this next time, okay?"
    Z "Continuemos con esto la próxima vez, ¿vale?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3284
translate spanish end_scene_nadia_d964521f:

    # Na "Alright, you win."
    Na "De acuerdo, tú ganas."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3285
translate spanish end_scene_nadia_0fa91180:

    # Na "See you at the dinner table, uncle."
    Na "Nos vemos en la cena, tío."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3288
translate spanish end_scene_nadia_7e133faf:

    # "You head back to the living room, where Omar and [W] are still talking."
    "Vuelves al salón, donde Omar y [W] siguen hablando."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3295
translate spanish end_scene_omar_e193d7d1:

    # Ra "Everyone? Dinner is ready!"
    Ra "¿Todos? ¡La cena está lista!"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3296
translate spanish end_scene_omar_6f1e10fa:

    # Ra "And Omar, please let Nadia know, will you?"
    Ra "Y Omar, por favor, avisa a Nadia, ¿quieres?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3299
translate spanish end_scene_omar_1f165809:

    # Om "Yes, of course sweetheart."
    Om "Sí, por supuesto, cariño."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3303
translate spanish end_scene_omar_95bee9bc:

    # "You continue the conversation for a while, before deciding to let your wife take over again..."
    "Continuáis la conversación durante un rato, antes de decidir que tu mujer vuelva a tomar el mando..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3312
translate spanish vf_dinner_89ca431c:

    # "Nothing special is happening during your stay, except for Rabiah being tense and quiet."
    "No ocurre nada especial durante vuestra estancia, excepto que Rabiah está tensa y callada."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3313
translate spanish vf_dinner_2178dc50:

    # "You start wondering if they resolved their issues from your last visit. And just then, the family dinner starts..."
    "Empiezas a preguntarte si habrán resuelto sus problemas de tu última visita. Y justo entonces, empieza la cena familiar..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3316
translate spanish vf_dinner_2054213d:

    # Om "My wife said she is coming back in a second. I think we can surely start eating. Enjoy!"
    Om "Mi mujer me ha dicho que vuelve enseguida. Creo que ya podemos empezar a comer. ¡Que aproveche!"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3318
translate spanish vf_dinner_41c0f2a6:

    # "You hear the door to the dining room open..."
    "Oyes abrirse la puerta del comedor..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3319
translate spanish vf_dinner_23c5ac88:

    # Ra "How nice of you to wait for me, husband..."
    Ra "Qué amable por tu parte esperarme, marido..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3322
translate spanish vf_dinner_ea644331:

    # "Rabiah walks into the room, and stands in the entrance for a second, wordlesly, until she is sure to have everybody's attention."
    "Rabiah entra en la habitación, y se queda de pie en la entrada durante un segundo, pensativa, hasta que se asegura de tener la atención de todo el mundo."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3325
translate spanish vf_dinner_6e5711d8:

    # Ra "I'm back."
    Ra "He vuelto."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3328
translate spanish vf_dinner_3b7fbff5:

    # "The change in her wardrobe is immediately noticeable. as she is showing considerably more skin."
    "El cambio en su vestuario se nota de inmediato, ya que enseña bastante más piel."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3331
translate spanish vf_dinner_d34bbdc7:

    # Na "M-mom...?"
    Na "¿Mamá...?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3332
translate spanish vf_dinner_8a157a27:

    # Om "Rabiah! What is the meaning of this?"
    Om "¡Rabiah! ¿Qué significa esto?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3335
translate spanish vf_dinner_b8f79a8a:

    # Na "Are you alright, mom?"
    Na "¿Te encuentras bien, mamá?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3336
translate spanish vf_dinner_a7c8810c:

    # "Nadia looks at her mother with a hint of worry on her otherwise excited expression."
    "Nadia mira a su madre con una pizca de preocupación en su expresión, por lo demás excitada."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3339
translate spanish vf_dinner_786a1139:

    # Ra "Never better, Nadia. Never better..."
    Ra "Nunca mejor, Nadia. Nunca mejor..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3342
translate spanish vf_dinner_1c65e75c:

    # "Rabiah smiles at her daughter. Something in her posture seems to have shifted, along with the change of clothing."
    "Rabiah sonríe a su hija. Algo en su postura parece haber cambiado, junto con el cambio de ropa."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3345
translate spanish vf_dinner_4aaa4115:

    # "Ignoring her husband, Rabiah sits down at the table, in her new clothes, a satisfied expression on her face."
    "Ignorando a su marido, Rabiah se sienta a la mesa, con su ropa nueva, y una expresión de satisfacción en el rostro."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3348
translate spanish vf_dinner_54a646f9:

    # Ra "[W], your last visit taught me something that I had forgotten."
    Ra "[W], tu última visita me enseñó algo que había olvidado."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3349
translate spanish vf_dinner_d76a8fcd:

    # Ra "It reminded me of my past and who I was before..."
    Ra "Me recordó mi pasado y quién era antes..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3352
translate spanish vf_dinner_c65f916d:

    # W "What do you mean?"
    W "¿Qué quieres decir?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3355
translate spanish vf_dinner_c275c56b:

    # Ra "Well, Omar and I have been talking about things."
    Ra "Bueno, Omar y yo hemos estado hablando de cosas."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3356
translate spanish vf_dinner_60649478:

    # Ra "{i}We{/i} came to the conclusion that I'm not really happy, and really haven't been for a while."
    Ra "{i}Llegamos{/i} a la conclusión de que no soy realmente feliz, y hace tiempo que no lo soy."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3357
translate spanish vf_dinner_6f275c53:

    # Ra "Following his demands... I mean, of course, our {i}rules{/i}... was fine where we used to live, but here it just makes us stand out, and not in a good way."
    Ra "Siguiendo sus exigencias... Quiero decir, claro, nuestras {i}reglas{/i}... estaban bien donde vivíamos, pero aquí sólo nos hacen destacar, y no en el buen sentido."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3360
translate spanish vf_dinner_3f2327fa:

    # Ra "But more than that, it's just the general situation. Like Nadia being forced to sneak around to have a bit of a life."
    Ra "Pero más que eso, es la situación general. Como que Nadia se viera obligada a escabullirse para tener un poco de vida."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3361
translate spanish vf_dinner_4daaf4c0:

    # Om "Eh... Rabiah..."
    Om "Eh... Rabiah..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3362
translate spanish vf_dinner_a0850e23:

    # "The man seems to bristle at the mention of Nadia ignoring his authority, but is quickly shushed by Rabiah."
    "El hombre parece erizarse ante la mención de que Nadia ignora su autoridad, pero Rabiah le hace callar rápidamente."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3363
translate spanish vf_dinner_53e249ee:

    # Ra "Let me finish, Omar!"
    Ra "¡Déjame terminar, Omar!"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3366
translate spanish vf_dinner_b3c2928e:

    # Om "Uh..."
    Om "Uhm..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3367
translate spanish vf_dinner_0491d447:

    # "He laughs nervously, trying to hide his embarrassment..."
    "Se ríe nerviosamente, intentando ocultar su vergüenza..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3370
translate spanish vf_dinner_2c745f80:

    # W "I think I understand what you mean, sister. Omar certainly seems to be a bit stiff, a bit set in his ways maybe."
    W "Creo que entiendo lo que quieres decir, hermana. Omar parece ciertamente un poco rígido, un poco inamovible tal vez."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3373
translate spanish vf_dinner_dce34d65:

    # Ra "Yes, well, it's a little hypocritical of him to ask us to be reserved and modest, and then stare at your tits half the time you're here."
    Ra "Sí, bueno, es un poco hipócrita por su parte pedirnos que seamos reservadas y modestas, y luego mirarte las tetas la mitad del tiempo que estás aquí."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3376
translate spanish vf_dinner_bd67f74f:

    # W "Well, yeah, he does have wandering eyes. Doesn't he?"
    W "Bueno, sí, tiene ojos errantes. ¿Verdad que sí?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3379
translate spanish vf_dinner_08cbe970:

    # "She smirks slighty..."
    "Ella sonríe levemente..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3380
translate spanish vf_dinner_a841367b:

    # Naw "Interesting stuff, isn't it..."
    Naw "Es interesante, ¿verdad?..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3383
translate spanish vf_dinner_aa2aa095:

    # "They continue chatting..."
    "Siguen charlando..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3384
translate spanish vf_dinner_a0172316:

    # W "Remember when we were younger and you were bringing guys home all the time? That would really have given him something to look at."
    W "¿Recuerdas cuando éramos más jóvenes y traías chicos a casa todo el tiempo? Eso sí que le habría dado algo en lo que fijarse."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3385
translate spanish vf_dinner_709a741f:

    # Ra "Eh, as you said, we were young."
    Ra "Eh, como dijiste, éramos jóvenes."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3386
translate spanish vf_dinner_9ccce96b:

    # W "More or less around Nadia's age... time flies, doesn't it? Makes you wonder if she's anything like you were."
    W "Más o menos de la edad de Nadia... El tiempo vuela, ¿verdad? Te hace preguntarte si ella es como eras tú."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3387
translate spanish vf_dinner_21b1a426:

    # Na "Are you asking me if I am bringing boys home? No! That's a headache I can do without."
    Na "¿Me estás preguntando si voy a traer chicos a casa? ¡No! Es un dolor de cabeza del que puedo prescindir."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3388
translate spanish vf_dinner_ef5c4392:

    # W "Boys, girls, that's really not for me to say..."
    W "Chicos, chicas, eso no me corresponde a mí decirlo..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3392
translate spanish vf_dinner_555ca686:

    # Na "Well, in any case I don't {i}bring{/i} them here..."
    Na "Bueno, en cualquier caso yo no {i}los traigo{/i} aquí..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3395
translate spanish vf_dinner_65079370:

    # "Nadia can't help but stare at you for quite some time, to which [W] can't help but laugh."
    "Nadia no puede evitar mirarte fijamente durante un buen rato, a lo que [W] no puede evitar reírse."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3397
translate spanish vf_dinner_555ca686_1:

    # Na "Well, in any case I don't {i}bring{/i} them here..."
    Na "Bueno, en cualquier caso yo no {i}los traigo{/i} aquí..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3400
translate spanish vf_dinner_28239e1b:

    # Ra "Anyway, we were having some difficulties, lately, even in our intimacy... but I expect that that will all change if we broaden our minds a little."
    Ra "En fin, últimamente estábamos teniendo algunas dificultades, incluso en nuestra intimidad... pero espero que todo eso cambie si ampliamos un poco nuestras mentes."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3401
translate spanish vf_dinner_ccdfbee8:

    # Ra "And Omar agrees with me, of course."
    Ra "Y Omar está de acuerdo conmigo, por supuesto."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3404
translate spanish vf_dinner_fe63e8fc:

    # "Omar doesn't seem to be at ease in the situation, which isn't really a surprise to you, as Rabiah makes sure that he can't get a word in the conversation."
    "Omar no parece estar a gusto en la situación, lo que en realidad no te sorprende, ya que Rabiah se asegura de que no pueda articular palabra en la conversación."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3407
translate spanish vf_dinner_0ad138e8:

    # "With something akin to resignation, Omar nods demurely."
    "Con algo parecido a la resignación, Omar asiente, recatado."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3408
translate spanish vf_dinner_bce10038:

    # Om "Yes, of course! I think it's..."
    Om "Sí, ¡por supuesto! Creo que lo es..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3409
translate spanish vf_dinner_26593aaa:

    # "With a little smirk, [W] speaks up again, interrupting him."
    "Con una pequeña sonrisa burlona, [W] vuelve a hablar, interrumpiéndole."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3412
translate spanish vf_dinner_f388e938:

    # W "Well, I am happy to see that my big sister is finding her old self again."
    W "Me alegra ver que mi hermana mayor vuelve a ser la de antes."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3413
translate spanish vf_dinner_19e8f613:

    # W "Who knows, maybe the new outfit is just the beginning of a new take on life. I can't wait to see where this will lead you."
    W "Quién sabe, quizá el nuevo atuendo sea sólo el principio de una nueva forma de ver la vida. Estoy deseando de ver adónde te lleva esto."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3418
translate spanish vf_dinner_4b771b98:

    # "Eventually, you prepare to go home."
    "Finalmente, te preparas para volver a casa."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3421
translate spanish vf_dinner_8ca31312:

    # Om "Well, this has been a nice dinner."
    Om "Ha sido una cena agradable."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3424
translate spanish vf_dinner_e23fe592:

    # W "Yes, it was nice... an interesting evening."
    W "Sí, ha sido... una velada interesante."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3427
translate spanish vf_dinner_dbd4fbf5:

    # Om "Interesting?"
    Om "¿Interesante?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3428
translate spanish vf_dinner_8c8a4887:

    # W "Surprising, then... I did not expect my big sister to come out of her shell all of a sudden."
    W "Sorprendente, pues... No esperaba que mi hermana mayor saliera de su caparazón de repente."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3431
translate spanish vf_dinner_0ea9b349:

    # Om "Oh, that... yes. I see. Well, she-..."
    Om "Oh, eso... sí. Ya veo. Bueno, ella..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3434
translate spanish vf_dinner_b956f29b:

    # "Omar's voice fizzles out when [W] shifts her posture, raising her shoulders just a little, and moving her weight from one leg to the other."
    "La voz de Omar se apaga cuando [W] cambia de postura, levanta un poco los hombros y mueve el peso de una pierna a la otra."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3437
translate spanish vf_dinner_22d98fdb:

    # W "She looks great, more so than her more... conservative clothes could possibly reveal. You are a very lucky man."
    W "Está estupenda, más de lo que su ropa más... conservadora podría revelar. Eres un hombre muy afortunado."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3438
translate spanish vf_dinner_07ea5ced:

    # Omw "Uh-hmm, yes... very lucky."
    Omw "Uhm... sí... muy afortunado."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3439
translate spanish vf_dinner_3513e658:

    # "Omar is zoning out at the sight in front of him, again. He looks at [W] both confused and excited."
    "Omar vuelve a perder el sentido ante lo que tiene delante. Mira a [W] confundido y excitado a la vez."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3442
translate spanish vf_dinner_f0a99654:

    # W "So really, I loved it. Seems that you cooked the meat extra spicy as well, sister."
    W "La verdad es que me ha encantado. Parece que también cocinaste la carne muy picante, hermana."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3443
translate spanish vf_dinner_c2b50c75:

    # Ra "Hm..."
    Ra "Hm..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3449
translate spanish vf_dinner_7c6e9f87:

    # Ra "..."
    Ra "..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3450
translate spanish vf_dinner_4792fb28:

    # "She looks disappointed..."
    "Parece decepcionada..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3453
translate spanish vf_dinner_59eba69d:

    # Ra "I guess the meal wasn't the only thing that he's impressed with..."
    Ra "Supongo que la comida no fue lo único que le impresionó..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3456
translate spanish vf_dinner_da71d5ef:

    # "Meanwhile, next to them..."
    "Mientras tanto, junto a ellos..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3459
translate spanish vf_dinner_b2192117:

    # Na "Well, tonight was full of surprises, after all."
    Na "Bueno, después de todo, esta noche ha estado llena de sorpresas."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3460
translate spanish vf_dinner_14ee5c9d:

    # Na "I figured it might turn out to be a boring dinner, but apparently my mother had other plans. That's so unlike her..."
    Na "Supuse que sería una cena aburrida, pero al parecer mi madre tenía otros planes. Eso no es propio de ella..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3464
translate spanish vf_dinner_93884786:

    # Z "I'm sure you did your part to motivate her."
    Z "Seguro que pusiste de tu parte para motivarla."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3468
translate spanish vf_dinner_0b27440f:

    # Na "I am pretty sure it wasn't just me {i}*giggles*{/i}."
    Na "Estoy bastante segura de que no fui sólo yo {i}*risitas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3469
translate spanish vf_dinner_b0600968:

    # Na "But yeah, I'm glad anyway, she's awesome now."
    Na "Pero sí, de todas formas me alegro, ahora ella es impresionante."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3470
translate spanish vf_dinner_fe724f1e:

    # Na "If nothing else, it means I won't have to go around her back anymore. We have been talking, lately..."
    Na "Si nada lo impide, significa que ya no tendré que rodear su espalda. Hemos estado hablando, últimamente..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3471
translate spanish vf_dinner_a27371b3:

    # Na "I do wonder though, if she truly wants to go back to her old way of life..."
    Na "Aunque me pregunto, si realmente quiere volver a su antigua forma de vida..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3477
translate spanish vf_dinner_1b338df2:

    # "She leans against you..."
    "Ella se apoya en ti..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3480
translate spanish vf_dinner_d287b473:

    # Na "And who will she set her eyes on, if she decides she wants to have a little fun?"
    Na "¿Y en quién pondrá sus ojos, si decide que quiere divertirse un poco?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3483
translate spanish vf_dinner_85770172:

    # Z "Don't tell me you're afraid of a little competition."
    Z "No me digas que te da miedo un poco de competencia."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3484
translate spanish vf_dinner_0a86146f:

    # "As your mouth opens in a cheeky grin, Nadia cuts your provocation short."
    "Cuando tu boca se abre en una sonrisa descarada, Nadia corta en seco tu provocación."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3487
translate spanish vf_dinner_4513dca9:

    # "As she moves forward again, moving her face close to yours, she whispers in a sultry tone..."
    "Mientras avanza de nuevo, acercando su cara a la tuya, te susurra en un tono sensual..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3488
translate spanish vf_dinner_1966d5f6:

    # Naw "Do you {i}really{/i} think it's a competition?"
    Naw "¿De {i}verdad{/i} crees que es una competición?"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3491
translate spanish vf_dinner_ad00add3:

    # "She leans into you, closing the distance even more."
    "Se inclina hacia ti, acortando aún más la distancia."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3494
translate spanish vf_dinner_5cceaa1f:

    # "Her lips part, slowly..."
    "Sus labios se separan, lentamente..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3497
translate spanish vf_dinner_60365b64:

    # "{i}*kissing*"
    "{i}*beso*{/i}"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3498
translate spanish vf_dinner_4f3f8b31:

    # Na "Mh..."
    Na "Mh..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3499
translate spanish vf_dinner_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3500
translate spanish vf_dinner_6f14fe43:

    # "Nadia kisses you passionately, as Omar seems to be still distracted by the sight in front of him."
    "Nadia te besa apasionadamente, mientras Omar parece seguir distraído por el espectáculo que tiene delante."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3501
translate spanish vf_dinner_23c0b75a:

    # "Someone else however is watching..."
    "Sin embargo, alguien más está mirando..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3504
translate spanish vf_dinner_492ef092:

    # "Standing next to her sister, Rabiah has noticed the intimate moment between her daughter and you."
    "De pie junto a su hermana, Rabiah se ha dado cuenta del momento íntimo entre su hija y tú."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3505
translate spanish vf_dinner_82be277d:

    # Ra "Nadia...!"
    Ra "¡Nadia...!"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3512
translate spanish vf_dinner_61fd4f6b:

    # Ra "Nadia... stop that..."
    Ra "Nadia... deja eso..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3515
translate spanish vf_dinner_6da676a3:

    # Na "{i}*sigh*{/i}"
    Na "{i}*suspiro*{/i}"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3516
translate spanish vf_dinner_93037790:

    # Na "Mom... I'm just saying goodbye..."
    Na "Mamá... Sólo me estoy despidiendo..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3519
translate spanish vf_dinner_dd9203eb:

    # "For a second, it looks like Rabiah is about to launch in a tirade aimed at Nadia, or possibly yourself..."
    "Por un segundo, parece que Rabiah está a punto de lanzar una reprimenda contra Nadia, o posiblemente contra ti mismo..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3522
translate spanish vf_dinner_9c61d205:

    # Ra "Just...{i}*sigh*{/i} just don't be so blatant."
    Ra "Simplemente... {i}*suspiro*{/i} no seas tan descarada."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3527
translate spanish vf_dinner_4f4f499e:

    # "It has been an interesting turn of events today, and you wonder where it will lead..."
    "Hoy ha sido un interesante giro de los acontecimientos, y te preguntas adónde conducirá..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3528
translate spanish vf_dinner_5806e1df:

    # "After you wave each other goodbye, you take the road back home."
    "Después de despediros, emprendéis el camino de vuelta a casa."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3536
translate spanish vf_dinner_4f4f499e_1:

    # "It has been an interesting turn of events today, and you wonder where it will lead..."
    "Hoy ha sido un interesante giro de los acontecimientos, y te preguntas adónde conducirá..."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3537
translate spanish vf_dinner_5806e1df_1:

    # "After you wave each other goodbye, you take the road back home."
    "Después de despediros, emprendéis el camino de vuelta a casa."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3544
translate spanish vf_dinner_2496c9fc:

    # " The dinner was quite awkward, but you and [W] didn't really care, as the tense drama in the air was entertaining enough."
    "La cena fue bastante incómoda, pero a ti y a [W] no os importó mucho, ya que el tenso drama que se respiraba en el ambiente era suficientemente entretenido."

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3545
translate spanish vf_dinner_a9e64d67:

    # "You both sensed that your sister-in-law and her husband had things to discuss once this was over."
