translate spanish vf_dinner_08cd6dad:

    # Ra "Before I married you, I would not be shamed into hiding. I would walk proud, my head held high, and if men or women wanted to look, I would have no shame!"
    Ra "Antes de casarme contigo, no me avergonzaba escondiéndome. Caminaba orgullosa, con la cabeza bien alta, y si los hombres o las mujeres querían mirar, ¡no me avergonzaba!"

# game/scripts/family.rpy:3624
translate spanish vf_dinner_749397f8:

    # Ra "No shame of showing the goods the gods blessed me with for all to see, instead of draping myself in layers of clothing, only for you to unpack whenever you remember or can be bothered to."
