translate spanish vf_end_a708d38b:

    # "You continued to eat dinner together. Not much later, [W] and you called it a day and said your goodbyes."
    "Seguís cenando juntos. No mucho más tarde, [W] y tú os disteis por satisfechos y os despedisteis."

